  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    JCHR reports on the detention of young people with learning disabilities or autism: government response
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Response to the Joint Committee on Human Rights (JCHR) recommendations on the rights of people with a learning disability or autistic young people in inpatient settings.</p>

  </div>
